{"video_id": "9rU41b2J7qs", "title": "058  The most important of all instructions of Srila Prabhupada", "speaker": "HDG Srila Prabhupada", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9rU41b2J7qs", "duration": 135, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 10.16, "text": " There was one devotee named Guru Kripa."}, {"start": 10.66, "end": 11.5, "text": " He was Swami Aditya."}, {"start": 11.98, "end": 12.98, "text": " He went to Prabhupada."}, {"start": 13.040000000000001, "end": 15.26, "text": " He says, Prabhupada, of all the things that you have taught,"}, {"start": 15.36, "end": 16.240000000000002, "text": " what is the most important?"}, {"start": 17.240000000000002, "end": 17.8, "text": " And Prabhupada says,"}, {"start": 17.86, "end": 26.76, "text": " That if you have firm faith in Guru and Krishna,"}, {"start": 26.76, "end": 28.52, "text": " then everything will be revealed to you."}, {"start": 30.0, "end": 31.6, "text": " Did anybody ever get a revelation"}, {"start": 31.6, "end": 32.7, "text": " that there's a higher understanding,"}, {"start": 32.82, "end": 33.58, "text": " a lower understanding?"}, {"start": 34.18, "end": 35.38, "text": " Where did that come from?"}, {"start": 35.9, "end": 38.42, "text": " Because if one does not hear submissively"}, {"start": 38.42, "end": 40.14, "text": " and has firm faith in your chara,"}, {"start": 40.18, "end": 41.7, "text": " he will develop some crazy idea."}, {"start": 42.08, "end": 43.32, "text": " You will manufacture something."}, {"start": 45.120000000000005, "end": 46.3, "text": " It's just like some people,"}, {"start": 46.4, "end": 47.44, "text": " they have manufactured an idea."}, {"start": 47.54, "end": 49.96, "text": " Oh, now we can re-edit Prabhupada's books"}, {"start": 49.96, "end": 52.28, "text": " and go to the monastery and redo the books."}, {"start": 52.82, "end": 53.019999999999996, "text": " Gotcha."}, {"start": 53.82, "end": 55.18, "text": " Prabhupada gave such instruction."}, {"start": 55.620000000000005, "end": 56.760000000000005, "text": " We wrote a letter."}, {"start": 56.760000000000005, "end": 58.64, "text": " Some devotees wrote a letter to them."}, {"start": 59.16, "end": 59.400000000000006, "text": " They say,"}, {"start": 59.4, "end": 63.16, "text": " Whether Prabhupada has given any direct verifiable evidence"}, {"start": 63.16, "end": 66.0, "text": " to go back to the manuscript and change the books."}, {"start": 66.98, "end": 67.52, "text": " They reply,"}, {"start": 67.62, "end": 69.2, "text": " We are not aware of this."}, {"start": 69.52, "end": 69.78, "text": " I says,"}, {"start": 69.84, "end": 72.02, "text": " Whether your GBC has ever found such instruction."}, {"start": 72.66, "end": 74.25999999999999, "text": " Nowhere we can find such instruction."}, {"start": 74.34, "end": 75.26, "text": " Then why you are changing?"}, {"start": 76.92, "end": 79.2, "text": " If Prabhupada has not given you instruction"}, {"start": 79.2, "end": 81.06, "text": " to go change his book"}, {"start": 81.06, "end": 83.14, "text": " with some grammatical embellishment program,"}, {"start": 83.25999999999999, "end": 83.94, "text": " why change it?"}, {"start": 84.94, "end": 86.24, "text": " When Prabhupada was there,"}, {"start": 86.24, "end": 87.1, "text": " there are so many scholars."}, {"start": 87.25999999999999, "end": 88.32, "text": " You read this Bhagavad Gita."}, {"start": 89.4, "end": 91.28, "text": " So many scholars have given nice reviews"}, {"start": 91.28, "end": 92.60000000000001, "text": " and appreciation of his books."}, {"start": 93.68, "end": 95.32000000000001, "text": " Amir Velas Maraj knows he was there."}, {"start": 96.06, "end": 96.44000000000001, "text": " You see?"}, {"start": 97.28, "end": 98.62, "text": " So many scholars would come."}, {"start": 99.02000000000001, "end": 100.2, "text": " Did any one of them complain?"}, {"start": 100.30000000000001, "end": 100.74000000000001, "text": " Oh, no."}, {"start": 101.08000000000001, "end": 101.92, "text": " This is not proper."}, {"start": 102.44000000000001, "end": 104.08000000000001, "text": " None of them would dare do that."}, {"start": 104.52000000000001, "end": 105.58000000000001, "text": " They all appreciate it."}, {"start": 106.96000000000001, "end": 108.68, "text": " Prabhupada has not given no such instruction"}, {"start": 108.68, "end": 110.06, "text": " that you go rewrite all the books."}, {"start": 111.08000000000001, "end": 112.7, "text": " Of course, those who claim that"}, {"start": 112.7, "end": 114.10000000000001, "text": " they have seen the truth,"}, {"start": 114.28, "end": 116.2, "text": " they have so-called higher understanding."}, {"start": 116.68, "end": 118.86000000000001, "text": " But we see that so-called higher understanding,"}, {"start": 119.4, "end": 121.06, "text": " is not based on the law book of ISKCON."}, {"start": 121.12, "end": 122.28, "text": " It is based on Manodharma."}, {"start": 122.44000000000001, "end": 124.0, "text": " Manodharma in Chaitanya Charitam"}, {"start": 124.0, "end": 125.88000000000001, "text": " is described as mental speculation."}, {"start": 126.58000000000001, "end": 128.36, "text": " He concocts something out of the thin air."}, {"start": 130.98000000000002, "end": 132.98000000000002, "text": " Manodharma"}]}